{
  "stem": "24268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tried, you know to-- they played while the people are screaming, the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she was in music after she escaped from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was on the underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I met her in Israel, so she told me that was the last transport in August, '43, when they liquidate the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they liquidate in the ghetto in '43, they sent all the Jews-- they didn't have time to segregate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was hoping still maybe, somebody, someone, somehow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister was so gorgeous, so young, youthful and full of life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mom, my cousins-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took the whole transport away, straight to the-- straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I wanted to say something else about happened in Peterswaldau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one of the [NON-ENGLISH]-- that means group, from the group Jewish girls were-- there were certain group what they had one on the top, I mean as the head group, the leader of the group.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the main of the-- there was 1,200 women and girls in this camp, Peterswaldau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Later they brought in from different camps to this camp, because they need, obviously, work to be done, help.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And she was Branca Weinstock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was the-- a blonde girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was very energetic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she was-- and first of all, the [GERMAN], the SS, the woman-- but she was in charge of all the Jews first.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If anything, she had first to go to her, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was always-- she was in charge of the Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the group girls-- she approached me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she asked me-- her name was [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gutka, ?] but I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two sisters, Gutka and the other one I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
